[section#res.on.required
    [:en] Required paragraph
    [:zh_CN] “要求”段落
]

[para]
[:en]
[%restriction]
Violation of the preconditions specified in a function[=']s [=Requires]
paragraph results in undefined behavior unless the function[=']s [=Throws]
paragraph specifies throwing an exception when the precondition is violated.
[:zh_CN]
[%限制]
当违反了在某函数的 [=Requires] 段落中指定的前条件时，除非该函数的 [=Throws] 段落
指定了当该前条件被违反时将抛出异常，否则将导致未定义的行为。
